> Why don't you tell him you'll pay the additional $200 in cash,
> collect-on-delivery?  This protects both of you; you don't get the bus
> unless he gets the extra $200, but he doesn't get the extra $200 until he
> delivers the bus. (Also, make sure to spell out how soon you expect to
> receive it for the extra $200.)
